profitable or semantically safe. With correct cost evaluation, the transform will
no longer fire spuriously on the provided reproducer, avoiding the incorrect
zeroinitializer replacement.\n\n5. Conclusion:\nThe immediate bug is the misuse
of FixedVectorType::get in foldShuffleOfBinops, passing a type where an element
count is required. Fixing this to use ShuffleDstTy->getNumElements() will correct
